    <entry>
      <title>Bootstrap4布局</title>
      <link href="/2021/11/25/Bootstrap4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/"/>
      <url>/2021/11/25/Bootstrap4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p><a href="https://v4.bootcss.com/docs/getting-started/introduction/">Bootstrap4 中文文档</a></p></blockquote><h2 id="Bootstrap4布局"><a href="#Bootstrap4布局" class="headerlink" title="Bootstrap4布局"></a>Bootstrap4布局</h2><h3 id="布局基础"><a href="#布局基础" class="headerlink" title="布局基础"></a>布局基础</h3><h4 id="布局容器"><a href="#布局容器" class="headerlink" title="布局容器"></a>布局容器</h4><ul><li>.container<ul><li>在每个断点发生变化，比 100% 的宽度略小点</li></ul></li><li>.container-fluid<ul><li>保持 100% 的宽度</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="响应式断点"><a href="#响应式断点" class="headerlink" title="响应式断点"></a>响应式断点</h4><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// Small devices (landscape phones, <span class="number">576px</span> and up)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@media</span> (<span class="attribute">min-width</span>: <span class="number">576px</span>) &#123; ... &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// Medium devices (tablets, <span class="number">768px</span> and up)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@media</span> (<span class="attribute">min-width</span>: <span class="number">768px</span>) &#123; ... &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// Large devices (desktops, <span class="number">992px</span> and up)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@media</span> (<span class="attribute">min-width</span>: <span class="number">992px</span>) &#123; ... &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// Extra large devices (large desktops, <span class="number">1200px</span> and up)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@media</span> (<span class="attribute">min-width</span>: <span class="number">1200px</span>) &#123; ... &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="网格系统"><a href="#网格系统" class="headerlink" title="网格系统"></a>网格系统</h3><h4 id="网格选项"><a href="#网格选项" class="headerlink" title="网格选项"></a>网格选项</h4><ul><li>.col<ul><li><strong>超小屏幕设备</strong>&lt;576px</li></ul></li><li>.col-sm-<ul><li><strong>小型屏幕设备</strong>≥576px</li></ul></li><li>.col-md-<ul><li><strong>中型屏幕设备</strong>≥768 像素</li></ul></li><li>.col-lg-<ul><li><strong>大型屏幕设备</strong>≥992px</li></ul></li><li>.col-xl-<ul><li><strong>超大型屏幕设备</strong>≥1200px</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="自动布局列"><a href="#自动布局列" class="headerlink" title="自动布局列"></a>自动布局列</h4><ul><li>等宽列</li><li>设置一个列宽</li><li>可变宽度内容</li><li>等宽多列</li></ul><h4 id="响应式类"><a href="#响应式类" class="headerlink" title="响应式类"></a>响应式类</h4><ul><li>覆盖所有设备</li><li>水平排列</li><li>混合搭配</li><li>删除边距<ul><li>.no-gutters消除边距</li></ul></li><li>列包装</li></ul><h4 id="重排序"><a href="#重排序" class="headerlink" title="重排序"></a>重排序</h4><p><strong>排列顺序</strong></p><ul><li>.order-1 ~ .order-12</li><li>.order-first 和 .order-last</li></ul><p><strong>列偏移</strong></p><ul><li><p>.offset-*-{0 ~ 11}</p></li><li><p>.ml-auto 和 .mr-auto 强制隔离两边距离</p></li></ul><h4 id="列嵌套"><a href="#列嵌套" class="headerlink" title="列嵌套"></a>列嵌套</h4><p>通过添加 .row 元素放在已存在的 .col-* 元素内</p><h3 id="布局工具类"><a href="#布局工具类" class="headerlink" title="布局工具类"></a>布局工具类</h3><p><strong>display 块属性定义</strong></p><p><strong>Flexbox 选项</strong></p><p><strong>外边距与内边距</strong></p><p><strong>切换显示和隐藏</strong></p><h2 id="Bootstrap4新布局"><a href="#Bootstrap4新布局" class="headerlink" title="Bootstrap4新布局"></a>Bootstrap4新布局</h2><h3 id="定义弹性盒子"><a href="#定义弹性盒子" class="headerlink" title="定义弹性盒子"></a>定义弹性盒子</h3><ul><li>.d-flex</li><li>.d-inline-flex</li></ul><h3 id="排列方向"><a href="#排列方向" class="headerlink" title="排列方向"></a>排列方向</h3><h4 id="水平方向排列"><a href="#水平方向排列" class="headerlink" title="水平方向排列"></a>水平方向排列</h4><ul><li>.flex-row</li><li>.flex-row-reverse</li></ul><h4 id="垂直方向排列"><a href="#垂直方向排列" class="headerlink" title="垂直方向排列"></a>垂直方向排列</h4><ul><li>.flex-column</li><li>.flex-column-reverse</li></ul><h3 id="内容排列"><a href="#内容排列" class="headerlink" title="内容排列"></a>内容排列</h3><ul><li>justify-content-start</li><li>justify-content-center</li><li>justify-content-end</li><li>justify-content-between</li><li>justify-content-around</li></ul><h3 id="项目对齐"><a href="#项目对齐" class="headerlink" title="项目对齐"></a>项目对齐</h3><ul><li>align-items-start</li><li>align-items-end</li><li>align-items-center</li><li>align-items-baseline</li><li>align-items-stretch</li></ul><h3 id="自动对齐"><a href="#自动对齐" class="headerlink" title="自动对齐"></a>自动对齐</h3><ul><li>align-self-start</li><li>align-self-end</li><li>align-self-center</li><li>align-self-baseline</li><li>align-self-stretch</li></ul><h3 id="自动相等"><a href="#自动相等" class="headerlink" title="自动相等"></a>自动相等</h3><ul><li>.flex-fill</li></ul><h3 id="等宽变换"><a href="#等宽变换" class="headerlink" title="等宽变换"></a>等宽变换</h3><ul><li>.flex-grow-0</li><li>.flex-grow-1</li><li>.flex-shrink-0</li><li>.flex-shrink-1</li></ul><h3 id="自动浮动"><a href="#自动浮动" class="headerlink" title="自动浮动"></a>自动浮动</h3><h4 id="水平方向浮动"><a href="#水平方向浮动" class="headerlink" title="水平方向浮动"></a>水平方向浮动</h4><ul><li>无 margin</li><li>.mr-auto</li><li>.ml-auto</li></ul><h4 id="垂直方向浮动"><a href="#垂直方向浮动" class="headerlink" title="垂直方向浮动"></a>垂直方向浮动</h4><ul><li>.align-item-*</li><li>.flex-cloumn</li></ul><h3 id="弹性布局-包裹"><a href="#弹性布局-包裹" class="headerlink" title="弹性布局-包裹"></a>弹性布局-包裹</h3><ul><li>.flex-nowrap</li><li>.flex-wrap</li><li>.flex-wrap-reverse</li></ul><h3 id="排列顺序"><a href="#排列顺序" class="headerlink" title="排列顺序"></a>排列顺序</h3><ul><li>order-{0 ~ 12}</li></ul><h3 id="对齐内容"><a href="#对齐内容" class="headerlink" title="对齐内容"></a>对齐内容</h3><ul><li>.align-content-start</li><li>.align-content-end</li><li>.align-content-center</li><li>.align-content-between</li><li>.align-content-around</li><li>.align-content-stretch</li></ul><h2 id="Bootstrap4核心工具库-CSS通用样式类"><a href="#Bootstrap4核心工具库-CSS通用样式类" class="headerlink" title="Bootstrap4核心工具库-CSS通用样式类"></a>Bootstrap4核心工具库-CSS通用样式类</h2><h3 id="文本处理"><a href="#文本处理" class="headerlink" title="文本处理"></a>文本处理</h3><h4 id="文本对齐"><a href="#文本对齐" class="headerlink" title="文本对齐"></a>文本对齐</h4><ul><li>.text-left</li><li>.text-center</li><li>.text-right</li><li>text-justify</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
